Floating Sheet (Experimental)

Floating Sheet component for React Native.

üéµ FloatingPlayer Props

PropTypeDefaultDescription
___experimentalbooleanfalseExperimental flag for internal use or testing.
imageImageURISourceundefinedImage displayed in the player (e.g., album cover).
isPresentedbooleanfalseWhether the floating player is currently visible.
showImageWhenExpandedbooleantrueIf true, the image remains visible when player is expanded.
renderMaximizedContent() => React.ReactNodeundefinedCustom content to render when the player is fully expanded.
renderMinimizedContent() => React.ReactNodeundefinedCustom content to render when the player is minimized.
customImageAnimation(animation: Animated.Value, defaults: Initials) => ViewStyle | Animated.ViewStyleundefinedCustom animation style for the player image during transitions.
onSheetDismiss() => voidundefinedCallback triggered when the player sheet is dismissed.

PropertyTypeDescription

marginTopAnimated.AnimatedInterpolation<number>Interpolated top margin.
marginLeftAnimated.AnimatedInterpolation<number>Interpolated left margin.
opacityAnimated.AnimatedInterpolation<number>Interpolated opacity.
initialMarginAnimated.AnimatedInterpolation<number>Interpolated initial margin (for layout tweaks).
